q´onxa jun oyaj kye aye mya b´a´n ky-b´inchb´en ex nimxix ky-b´inchb´en.
Aye tatb´aj n-chi kyqanin qeye tun t-xi kyi´n ky-k´wale tze´nku
xnaq´tzanjtz, extzen tzaj kyq´o´n ky-chjo´n b´a´n,
mas toj kywa, aye mya b´a´n n-ku q-b´inchen
n-chi b´isun tun q-ch´iy moqa tun q-jyet qjunalx.
Toj tkyaqil, aye q´ij lu tb´anel qeye, extzen
aye mas meb´a qeye at ky-pwaq tun ky-b´inchen extzen tun ky-b´inchen
q´onxa pwaq te chojb´il, extzen amb´il tun t-xi b´inchet tb´anil tiyjil noq
