Ax tok, n-xob´e qa aye trolls n-chi b´inchan ikyjo,
axpe ikx qeju oʼkx jun kywiʼ teyele junjun. Texlena
tej t-xi tb´i´n tkyaqil jlu Bilbo il ti´j tu´n tb´ant tu´n
