goblins, extzen n-chi q´ojin kyi´j goblins.
n-xob´e qa atzun b´ajsb´il maj n-chi ky-ka´yin
kye qeju tb´anel tal chej, kyxol qe jlu at jun jolly
jun tal xjal saq t-xilen aju otoq txi tq´o´n Elrond te
