Ax ikx kykyaqil txqantl e jaw tzeʼn. Tb´ajlenxi tkyaqil kye
b´aj ky-el jun tb´anil ky-b´inchb´en, noqtzun aye otaq che kub´ kyb´yo´n aju´ nim toklen
Goblin extzen nimku txqantl, extzen
kykyaqil otoq che el oq, tuʼntzunju jaku txi qʼamet qa
