ponies extzen n-chi ky-meltz´aj ky-wi´ tun ky-jaye. Yupin
in che bʼettoq tukʼil tzalajbʼil, ik tzeʼn in che tzalajxix tuʼn tkubʼ kyqʼoʼn ky
t-xu´k t-xe t-xlekumal Mirkwood. Ik tza´n kye
xi´ Bilbo b´a´n t-ximan qa jun tiyjil
ik tzaʼn jun oso kyaj ttzaqpiʼn t-xlekumal tzeʼ ex
n-chi b´et jun rat kyi´j.
Jalin a Gandalf ax ikx xi tq´ama´n b´a´n t-xilen. Bilbo kub´ qe twitz
aju tx´otx´ n-chi tzalajxix extzen n-chi tzalaj ti´j
attaq ttxlaj ajq´ij tib´aj t-chej nim twa´lil. Attoq
