“Aye q´aq´ n-chi etz juntl majl tzalu,
ex mas nim kybʼet twitz alkyexku juntl maj».
Kykyaqil e jaw ẍchʼin. Atzun, ax tok, mya
najchaq ateʼtoq nimku spikʼun in che qoptzʼaj, ex
