¡N-chi yolin kyi´j aye enanos!
“Jun q´oj nimxix, noqtzun ayetzi´n b´a´n t-xilen,” chi
jun. “Titzen nya b´a´n ky-chib´jel ky-chib´jel
ax tok, noqtzun tu´nj, n-xi nq´ama´ne qa at jun tb´anil jugo toj.
“Ax tok, k-xel ky-b´inchen jun tb´anil wab´j, aj t-xi ky-b´inchen
tzaj t-xo´n ch´in, chi juntl.
“Mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi t-xo´na nim amb´il,” chi jun toxin.
“Mya ky-b´a´n ky-b´is tze´nku t-xilen. S'e'n tz'un taya
n-xi nq´o´ne kywa jun xjal b´a´nxix toj amb´il ja´lo, b´a´n tu´n t-ximane.
“Kyb´yo´na, n-xi nq´ama´ne,” chi jun tkyajin; “kyb´yo´na
jalin extzen ky-okx ky-k´u´n kyimni toj jun amb´il.
“O che kyim jalin, n-xi nq´o´ne t-xilen,” chi a
tnejil.
“Qa mya ikyjo. n-ka´yine jun n-chi b´et
noq jalin. Noq n-chi ul juntl majl, b´a´n tu´n t-xi nq´ama´ne,
t-xelju jun tb´anil watl. Kxel nyekʼune teya».
tuk´e jun kyxol aye arañas gordas n-chi b´et t-xe jun
k´uxb´il tzmaxi aj tpon junlaj t-xaq t-xaq t-xaq toj jun
t-xe jun t-xaq tze´ nim twa´lil. Bilbo tzaj t-xob´il,
