mya t-xilen,” chi Roäc, “exttzen n-xob´e qa mya b´a´n
q´oj toj chq´ajlaj. mya n-ok nq´o´ne tb´i te consej lu
b´a´n. Maske jun xjal mya b´a´n ky-b´is, mya
b´a´n tu´n t-xi t-kamb´an aju´ t-xjalil n-chi tzaj t-xob´a; ex
