b´incha´n ex mya b´incha´n, xi q´o´n te Bard;
tuʼnju tqʼama Dain jlu: «Kʼokel qqʼoʼne toklen aju yol kyaj bʼant tiʼj kyuʼn
aye kyimni, extzen jalin at Arkenstone toj t-xmilal
n-chi xq´uqin.
Axpe ikx jun kyajlaj t-xilen q´inumal
nimxix ma'xix, mas ma' toclen cywitz nim xjal
