Te Bilbo xi tq´ama´n: “Aju´ tesoro lu´ t-xilen
teya ik tza´n weye; maske ojtxi yol kyaj b´ant ti´j
mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi´ we´, qu´n nimxix xjal at jun ky-xim ti´j
q´oj extzen q´oj. Noqtzun tu´nj, maske teya
waje tu´n t-xi nq´o´ne tkyaqil t-xjelb´itza, b´a´n tu´n t-xi nq´o´ne
qa aye tyol Thorin, aye tzaj t-xob´il ti´j,
mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi yek´unte qa ax tok: tu´n t-xi qq´o´ne teya
b´otz´. N-chi tzaj nq´o´ne jun oyaj teya twitz tkyaqil.
“Nimxix t-xtalb´ila,” chi Bilbo. “exttzen axix tok
jun tzalajb´il te weye. ¿Titzen twitz tx´otx´ il ti´j tu´n t-xi n-k´amo´ne
tkyaqilju tesoro jay mya at q´oj ex b´iyb´il
