“B´a´n tzalajb´il kye tze´, akux at twitz tx´otx´
kuxin! ¡Ex che tzalaj kykyaqil qe t-xjalila!»
"Mankasab´il! O Gandalf! chi rey. "Kb´entil tuna
tkyaqil maj in kubʼ tyekʼina tibʼa jatumel mas il tiʼj tuʼn ttena
ex mya b´a´n n-ximana! Aju mas nim maj in kubʼ tyekʼina tibʼa toj
aye n-jaye mas b´a´n n-chin tzalaje!
“n-chin kub´sane teya,” chi Bilbo n-chi b´aj t-xob´il extzen
waʼl tiʼj jun tqan, «tuʼn t-xi tkʼamoʼn oyaj lu!». ex
etz tiʼn jun collar saq pwaq ttxʼotxʼil ex perla
aju otoq tzaj tqʼoʼn Dain te toj kypaʼn kyibʼ.
«¿Alkye tten o tzʼok nkʼamoʼne jun oyaj ik tzeʼn jlu, O
hobbit? chi rey. “B´a´n, er, n-ximane, mya b´i´n tza´n teya,” chi
Bilbo tzaj t-xob´il, “a, er, junjun ch´in t-xel
il ti´j tu´n t-xi b´inchet tun t-xi t-k´amo´na, er, t-xtalb´ila. a kxel nmane
